XML-EasySQL version 1.0
========================

A two-way SQL/XML base class for Perl. It was written by Curtis Lee Fulton
(http://fultron.net, curtisf@fultron.net).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

XML::DOM

